<div class=WordSection1 style='layout-grid:15.6pt'>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>Apache</span></b><b><span
style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>配置文件</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:200%'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>Apache</span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>的配置文件默认路径是“<span lang=EN-US>/etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf</span>”，编辑该文件就可以修改<span
lang=EN-US>Apache</span>的配置<span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>1</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置网页主目录，参数<span
lang=EN-US>DocumentRoot</span>就是网页存放的主目录。打开配置文件<span lang=EN-US>httpd.conf</span>，查找<span
lang=EN-US>DocumentRoot</span>（大约<span lang=EN-US>292</span>行）</span></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:14.9pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.9pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># DocumentRoot:
  The directory out of which you will serve your</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># documents. By
  default, all requests are taken from this directory, but</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># symbolic links
  and aliases may be used to point to other locations.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>DocumentRoot
  &quot;/var/www/html&quot;&nbsp;&nbsp; //</span></code><code><span
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:DengXian'>当前默认是在</span></code><code><span
  lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>&quot;/var/www/html&quot;</span></code><code><span
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:DengXian'>目录下，所有的网页必须放在这里</span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>2</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置连接端口，通过参数<span
lang=EN-US>listen</span>来设置连接的端口，默认<span lang=EN-US>80.</span>（大约<span
lang=EN-US>136</span>行）</span></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:14.9pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.9pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># Listen: Allows
  you to bind Apache to specific IP addresses and/or</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># ports, in
  addition to the default. See also the &lt;VirtualHost&gt;</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># directive.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># Change this to
  Listen on specific IP addresses as shown below to </span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># prevent Apache
  from glomming onto all bound IP addresses (0.0.0.0)</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#Listen
  12.34.56.78:80</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>Listen 80</span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>3</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置连接超时，参数<span
lang=EN-US>timeout</span>，当连接超过一定的空闲时间，就会自动断开。（大约<span lang=EN-US>68</span>行）</span></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:15.05pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:15.05pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># Timeout: The
  number of seconds before receives and sends time out.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>Timeout 60</span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>4</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置字符集，参数</span><code><span
lang=EN-US style='line-height:200%;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>AddDefaultCharset</span></code><code><span
style='line-height:200%;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>，建议最好设置<span lang=EN-US>utf-8</span>，这是通用的。（大约<span
lang=EN-US>753</span>行）</span></code></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:60.3pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:60.3pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># Specify a
  default charset for all content served; this enables</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># interpretation
  of all content as UTF-8 by default.&nbsp; To use the </span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># default browser
  choice (ISO-8859-1), or to allow the META tags</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># in HTML content
  to override this choice, comment out this</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># directive:</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>AddDefaultCharset
  UTF-8</span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>5</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置服务器名称，参数<span
lang=EN-US>ServerName</span>。这是服务器的域名，必须有<span lang=EN-US>dns</span>解析才可以访问。如果你没有合法的域名，那么只能通过<span
lang=EN-US>ip</span>地址来访问</span></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:74.3pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:74.3pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># ServerName
  gives the name and port that the server uses to identify itself.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># This can often
  be determined automatically, but we recommend you specify</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># it explicitly
  to prevent problems during startup.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># If this is not
  set to valid DNS name for your host, server-generated</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># redirections
  will not work.&nbsp; See also the UseCanonicalName directive.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># If your host
  doesn't have a registered DNS name, enter its IP address here.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># You will have
  to access it by its address anyway, and this will make </span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># redirections
  work in a sensible way.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#ServerName
  www.example.com:80</span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>6</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置<span
lang=EN-US>keepalive</span>，提高网络效率，默认是关闭的。（大约<span lang=EN-US>76</span>行）</span></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:14.9pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.9pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># KeepAlive:
  Whether or not to allow persistent connections (more than</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># one request per
  connection). Set to &quot;Off&quot; to deactivate.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>KeepAlive Off</span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:
"Microsoft YaHei"'>7</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei"'>、设置<span
lang=EN-US>keepaliverequest</span>，设置为<span lang=EN-US>0 </span>的时候没有限制，不过最好还是用默认值，或者自己根据情况来改变。（大约<span
lang=EN-US>83</span>行）</span></p>

<table class=a0 border=1 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="97%"
 style='width:97.0%;margin-left:24.1pt;border-collapse:collapse;border:none'>
 <tr style='height:14.9pt'>
  <td width=415 valign=top style='width:414.5pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
  background:#E7E6E6;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.9pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#
  MaxKeepAliveRequests: The maximum number of requests to allow</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># during a
  persistent connection. Set to 0 to allow an unlimited amount.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'># We recommend
  you leave this number high, for maximum performance.</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>#</span></code></p>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:200%'><code><span lang=EN-US
  style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:Menlo'>MaxKeepAliveRequests
  100&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></code></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
</table>

